{
  "texts": [
    "A study using a hybrid deep learning model that combined word-emoji embeddings showed improvements in sarcasm detection by better-capturing context (Kumar A. et al., 2023).",
    "This model highlights the role of emojis in expressing sarcasm, allowing the NLP system to understand the underlying sentiment of social media interactions.",
    "These findings emphasize the need for NLP models to go beyond traditional text analysis and incorporate multimodal and symbolical cues to accurately detect sarcasm in text.",
    "Another significant challenge in Natural Language Processing (NLP) is managing contextual ambiguity and cultural nuances.",
    "Words and phrases can have different meanings depending on the context, leading to potential misunderstandings by NLP systems."
  ]
}